    "Multiple Whisper backends: Whisper, Whisper.cpp, Faster Whisper, HuggingFace",
    "GPU acceleration support (CUDA for Nvidia, Apple Silicon, Vulkan)",
    "Export transcripts to TXT, SRT, and VTT formats",
